reviews.review_text: A superb AUD pull! To fully appreciate the quality of this recording, pay attention to the tail end of Stella Blue (right around the 6-minute mark) when the only thing seeping through the PA is the sound of Jerry's voice as he sings the final lines of the tune.  It's breathtaking~
